    <item>
      <title>里夫斯誓言“修正方向”以恢复英国的财富</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/reeves-vows-course-correction-to-restore-uk-economic-fortunes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[反对党工党候任财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯承诺对英国经济进行根本性的“路线修正”，称英国需要投资于增长并解决根本的结构性问题，以打破停滞的束缚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/reeves-vows-course-correction-to-restore-uk-economic-fortunes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 18:57:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙社会党表示他们不太可能支持AD的预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/portugal-socialists-say-they-re-unlikely-to-back-an-ad-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙社会党领袖佩德罗·努诺·桑托斯表示，他的政党“实际上不可能”同意由中右翼 AD 联盟组成的新政府提出的 2025 年预算，该联盟在 3 月 10 日以微弱优势赢得了选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/portugal-socialists-say-they-re-unlikely-to-back-an-ad-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 18:35:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>道格·埃姆霍夫谴责特朗普对犹太民主党人的“反犹太主义”评论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/emhoff-decries-antisemitic-trump-comments-on-jewish-democrats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[第二位先生道格·埃姆霍夫谴责共和党唐纳德·特朗普指责支持民主党的犹太人仇恨他们的宗教和以色列。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/emhoff-decries-antisemitic-trump-comments-on-jewish-democrats</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 18:26:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国警告全国供水系统遭受网络攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/us-warns-of-cyberattacks-against-water-systems-throughout-nation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府警告各国警惕针对供水系统的网络攻击，并指出与伊朗和中国政府有关的黑客正在持续发出威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/us-warns-of-cyberattacks-against-water-systems-throughout-nation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 18:13:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院允许德克萨斯州驱逐拜登出境法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/supreme-court-allows-texas-migrant-deportation-law-in-biden-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院允许德克萨斯州开始逮捕和驱逐非法入境者，拒绝阻止一项新法律，拜登政府称该法律将前所未有地侵犯联邦制定移民政策的权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/supreme-court-allows-texas-migrant-deportation-law-in-biden-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 18:10:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞内加尔总统表示延迟投票骚乱后民主完好无损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/senegal-s-sall-says-democracy-intact-after-delayed-vote-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞内加尔总统麦基·萨勒为自己推迟选举的决定进行了辩护，该决定使这个西非国家陷入了混乱，并坚称其民主和制度完好无损。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/senegal-s-sall-says-democracy-intact-after-delayed-vote-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 17:19:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德谴责德克萨斯基金撤资 85 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/texas-school-fund-pulls-8-5-billion-investment-from-blackrock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州周二决定从贝莱德公司 (BlackRock Inc.) 剥离 85 亿美元——引用投资公司的化石燃料政策——此举遭到了全球最大资产管理公司的严厉谴责，称这将在财务上损害该州的学校。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/texas-school-fund-pulls-8-5-billion-investment-from-blackrock</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 16:00:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港通过新保安法案引发海外警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/hong-kong-passes-local-security-bill-cementing-china-s-control</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港已快速进入国内安全立法，引发美国、欧盟和英国的新警告，称此举可能会压制这个全球金融中心的公开讨论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/hong-kong-passes-local-security-bill-cementing-china-s-control</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 10:55:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普 2024 年竞选总统期间的法律案件时间表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-trump-trials-court-dates-legal-timeline/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普正在竞选重返白宫，同时面临多项迫在眉睫的刑事和民事审判——美国历史上没有其他候选人面临过这样的挑战。这些法律时间表有助于理解这一切]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-trump-trials-court-dates-legal-timeline/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 10:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
